{"tid":2411028,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣海軍陸戰隊聯同海巡署三月將在東沙及太平島進行聯合軍事演習","createTime":"2021-02-17T05:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T06:04:42.000Z","uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8cd2fdb4e80b0f55bb278bc6060ee04e1df3c5d","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"由於去年曾傳出中共解放軍將要在南海進行「奪島」，因此目前我東沙島及南沙太平島已有海軍陸戰隊官兵移地訓練與駐防，因此，3月的演訓也將是海巡署與海軍陸戰隊今年首度執行聯合軍事演練，確保未來若遭受中共威脅，我軍有足夠防衛戰力。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n實彈射擊之所以受到關注，除了相關水域持續處於高度爭議外，去年曾有外媒報導，共軍可能奇襲攻佔上述兩座島嶼，一時間，這些超遠外離島如何防禦、如何在被攻佔後規復，社會高度關注，而後隨著總統蔡英文「越洋」連線東沙指揮部，曝光陸戰隊99旅一加強連兵力進駐當地，表面上以訓練為名，實際上也有強化該島防禦能力作用。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n從過去曝光的資訊顯示，海巡在東南沙至少裝備手、步槍等輕兵器，以及直射的機槍、40榴彈機槍和曲射的120公厘迫砲等。在狀況提升時，會從本島前推155公厘榴砲緊急部署，而在陸戰兵力重新登島後，也有可能將火力更強的肩射防空飛彈、小型偵蒐無人機帶至當地，惟此類火砲射擊仍應以傳統武器為主。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210216/S2LHQB7IPJGFRIU5J2D3OLWPIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210216%2FS2LHQB7IPJGFRIU5J2D3OLWPIY%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN294xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=a4adfee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210216%2FS2LHQB7IPJGFRIU5J2D3OLWPIY%2F&h=b4730809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210216/S2LHQB7IPJGFRIU5J2D3OLWPIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/new7/article/3480344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Fnew7%2Farticle%2F3480344&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN294xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=89472258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/new7/article/3480344</a>"},{"pid":"8edef9a49725395984f601e3826c22ab814957b3","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"海軍陸戰隊應該有廿幾年冇係南海軍演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次應該廿幾三十年前"},{"pid":"c9b690191d023733f8a23bad66c1b45965fa616f","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0430d998aadda933066c01c5444c28ba8db040","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d61cf569e8d21fb82493e338acc16a0a41f1cb2","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"加強防務都係好事"},{"pid":"75df399006397ddc7388511eebb4cd0ee504ebfc","tid":2411028,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"軍方高層人士今天指出，因應國家安全需要，蔡總統指示中科院要加速包括弓三丶雄三飛彈在內的各式武器系統量產任務，今年將是量產任務的高峰期，中科院院長張忠誠也向中科院全體員工發出新春談話，要求院內各單位在面對量產任務時要切記，不得操之過急，必須要恪遵工作安全紀律，按照標準作業程序執行，沒有安全就沒有一切。<br />\n<br />\n相關人士說，除了天弓三型防空飛彈丶雄風三型超音速反艦飛彈等武器系統進入量產之外，還有部分通過作戰測評的新式武器系統，今年將進行小批量生產階段。據了解，這部分包括陸射型天劍二型飛彈系統，以及<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">針對未曾對外公開丶但已實際撥交部隊部署的特殊飛彈系統，要進行性能提升後的小批量生產。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset